00:48:20.320 --> 00:48:22.560
Basically, if you can log into Posit Connect,

00:48:22.560 --> 00:48:23.760
you can view this content.

00:48:23.760 --> 00:48:25.679
So I'd pretty much be all Posit employees.

00:48:26.479 --> 00:48:29.840
Or I can say anyone, no login required.

00:48:29.840 --> 00:48:32.639
And that basically means if you have access to this URL

00:48:32.639 --> 00:48:34.159
you see at the top of your screen,

00:48:34.159 --> 00:48:35.600
you have access to this content.

00:48:36.239 --> 00:48:38.080
You'll also notice this URL is pretty ugly.

00:48:38.080 --> 00:48:39.919
